## MergeAgents Function — Merge Logic

| Scenario | Behavior |
|----------|----------|
| Non-unity agent exists | ALWAYS preserved (never overwritten) |
| Unity-* agent exists with model | Preserved (unless force=true) |
| Unity-* agent exists WITHOUT model | Gets preset model from provider |
| New unity-* agent | Added with preset model |
| force=true | Overwrites everything |

